OL,3,CBurnham says 'Manchester-ism' can
OL,4,Ctransform the whole of UK
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has said his vision of
OL,7,F"Manchester-ism" could mark "the end
OL,8,Fof neo-liberalism" as he defended his
OL,9,Fdecision to stand in the upcoming
OL,10,FMakerfield by-election.
OL,12,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester is
OL,13,Fseeking a return to Westminster after
OL,14,FLabour MP Josh Simons announced he
OL,15,Fwould stand down, triggering the
OL,16,Fcontest in the Greater Manchester
OL,17,Fconstituency.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@PO]oD@]OUpD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
